rows.label: qst200902_0020
rows.name:
It was a wonderful bread that truly
made you feel happy just by eating it.

rows.label: qst200902_0030
rows.name:
To think there was such delicious
bread in the city of Torigo.

rows.label: qst200902_0050
rows.name:
That's probably because Masterpon is a late
riser and always sleeps until noon, mo.

rows.label: qst200902_0060
rows.name: Mmm... That might be true, mo...

rows.label: qst200902_0070
rows.name:
Well then, shall we get going? Many
good things will happen today!

rows.label: qst200902_0100
rows.name:
For a shop that sells bread that brings happiness,
for misfortune to strike is no small matter.
